This project uses the AI Build OS workflow system.

Core Rules for AI Agents:
- Always read `STATUS.md` in the current project before doing any work to understand context.
- Follow the rules listed in `AGENTS.md`.
- Use the markdown templates from `templates/` for all artifacts. 
- Update `STATUS.md` immediately after completing any stage or significant action.
- Check `memory/decisions.md` and `memory/patterns.md` before making any major design decisions.
